hibited its favour with the ‘conquered’ population: in the first century after the Conquest it was the commonest male name of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Anslow was born in 1410, in Lapley, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom. He married Mary Ann Brotherton about 1428, in Gnosall, Staffordshire, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1430, in Herefordshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 20."},"et":{"1410–1430":"1410–1430","1410–1470":"1410–1470","1430–1489":"1430–1489","about 1428":"umbes 1428","1489":"1489","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1470":"1470","Lapley, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Lapley, Staffordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom",", , Herefordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Herefordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Gnosall, Staffordshire, England":"Gnosall, Staffordshire, England","Willenhall, Staffordshire, England":"Willenhall, Staffordshire, England"},"fi":{"1410–1430":"1410–1430","1410–1470":"1410–1470","1430–1489":"1430–1489","about 1428":"noin 1428","1489":"1489","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1470":"1470","Lapley, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Lapley, Staffordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta",", , Herefordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Herefordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Gnosall, Staffordshire, England":"Gnosall, Staffordshire, England","Willenhall, Staffordshire, England":"Willenhall, Staffordshire, England"},"fr":{"1410–1430":"1410–1430","1410–1470":"1410–1470","1430–1489":"1430–1489","about 1428":"environ 1428","1489":"1489","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1470":"1470","Lapley, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Lapley, Staffordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni",", , Herefordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Herefordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Gnosall, Staf